         patient_has_undergone_anticoagulant_therapy_with_enoxaparin_now@@administered_as_thromboprophylaxis_therapy@@identified_by_code@@temporalcontext_within_day_prior_to_or_two_days_after_cancer_related_surgery_during_index_hospitalization
