     :named REQ3_COMPONENT0_PRESCREEN_NOTES_MUST_COMPLETELY_SUFFICE)) ;; "To be included, the patient must have ((a code for anticoagulant treatment with dalteparin as thromboprophylaxis therapy (during the day prior to or two days after cancer-related surgery (during the index hospitalization))) OR (a code for anticoagulant treatment with enoxaparin as thromboprophylaxis therapy (during the day prior to or two days after cancer-related surgery (during the index hospitalization))) OR (a code for anticoagulant treatment with fondaparinux as thromboprophylaxis therapy (during the day prior to or two days after cancer-related surgery (during the index hospitalization))) OR (a code for anticoagulant treatment with unfractionated heparin as thromboprophylaxis therapy (during the day prior to or two days after cancer-related surgery (during the index hospitalization))))"
